fields.title: Python Job
fields.description:
I am looking for an experienced Python developer to assist me with web development tasks.

Specifically, I have existing code that needs to be worked on, so familiarity with working on existing projects is crucial.

The timeline for this project is immediate, with a deadline of less than 1 week.

Ideal skills and experience for this job include:

- Strong proficiency in Python programming
- Experience with web development frameworks such as Django or Flask
- Knowledge of HTML, CSS, and JavaScript
- Familiarity with database management systems such as MySQL or PostgreSQL
- Ability to work efficiently and meet tight deadlines

fields.title: Javascript Job
fields.description:
Minecraft Render Image

I am looking for a skilled graphic designer who can create a render image for my website
www.minecraft-heads.com

This image should roughly be 700px width and 350px high and show a few rendered characters decorating with heads and armorstands in Minecraft. For example one could place a head (like a treasure chest or so) on a block, the other one could put a human head on an armorstand which wear a leather outfit already. Some other heads are maybe also already visible around the two.

The background is kinda unimportant: Either it's fully transparent or you see it partially and it fades out to transparency. It's important that the render image is no a rectangular image or so, it should fade out to transparency (example: http://prntscr.com/DhhpCpQU0bOC)

I dont really have a good idea for a render image, that's why I'm placing this job.

If you apply for this job, please describe your rough idea, maybe even do a short draft on paper or so and show an example from your Minecraft render images.
